Name: VOC Caf√©
Review Text: Best authentic lamprais served here. Sells out pretty fast. Frozen lamprais also available. Priced at Rs. 505/- each. homemade ginger beer is recommended. They also serve kottu and hoppers for dinner. Burgers also available. Parking available. Seats about 16 in the AC area. 20- 30 outside.

Name: VOC Caf√©
Review Text: Ordered a chicken lamprais via their delivery partner appigo, Don't get fooled by the small size of the packet. The rice is tightly packed and enough for a person. The rice has the authentic taste along with the rest of the curries, however missed the egg. Well def order again

Name: VOC Caf√©
Review Text: A great place to get authentic lamp rice. Friendly staff tasty food. They have great sandwiches and some awesome homemade fesh juicy prices are reasonable and service is quick. Will recommend for anyone who was a quick bit, lunch or dinner. they have great pork sandwiches.

Name: VOC Caf√©
Review Text: Old workplace. Authentic homemade Lamprais, Homemade ginger beer and iced coffee and the homemade icecreams, Southern Fried Chicken Burger was what I know those days were authentic and recommended. 1 more homemade drink available occasionaly that you gotta check with the cafe.

Name: VOC Caf√©
Review Text: Some of the items from the menu was not available,  waiting time was way too long for the food to arrive; especially when the order was basic. The waiter gentleman didn't know what is available on that day,  so we placed the order and had to change the items thereafter..

Name: VOC Caf√©
Review Text: Had a bacon and egg pastry which was great. Had a good quantity of bacon and was worth the money. Ordered a 'frozen' strawberry cheesecake ice cream for dessert. This was the worst Rs250 spent! Sickeningly sweet and doused with artificial colouring and flavours, it neither tasted like strawberry or cheesecake!

Name: VOC Caf√©
Review Text: The garden area provides the perfect ambience for relaxation while enjoying a cool beer. Great food but the portions could improve in proportion to the cost. Friendly and courteous staff who may find it difficult to cope during during weekends.

Name: VOC Caf√©

Name: VOC Caf√©
